\id 1TI ‑ Ikizu 1 Timothy
\h 1 Timoseo
\toc3 1 Timoseo
\toc2 1 Timoseo
\toc1 Ɨnyarʉbha ye embere ya Paaurʉ kwa Timoseo
\mt2 Ɨnyarʉbha ye embere ya Paaurʉ kwa
\mt1 Timoseo
\imt1 Ʉbhʉkangati
\ip Ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ yandikirwɨ na Paaurʉ. Akamwandɨkɨra ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ aarɨ arabhirikirwa Timoseo. Timoseo akasabhʉka kʉnzɨra ye emeremo ja Paaurʉ, necho kigiriryɨ Paaurʉ arabhɨrɨkɨra Timoseo, umwana waazɨ wa amaheene mubhwisirirya. Timoseo akagenda na Paaurʉ momeremo myaru ju ukurwaza Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu igʉrʉ wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ (\xt Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 17:14‑15, 18:5\xt*). Hanʉ Paaurʉ aarɨ akɨɨrɨ araandɨka ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ, akamoha Timoseo emeremo ju ukwimɨɨrɨrɨra abhiisirirya mʉrʉbhɨri rwa Efeeso.
\ip Kɨnʉ chagiriryɨ Paaurʉ aandɨkɨ ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ, yaarɨ kʉbhʉʉrɨra Timoseo chɨmbu ikwenderwa korobhora na kwija abhaangariri na abhasakirya bha risengerero. Paaurʉ akeenda abhaangariri bhabhɨ bhagʉrʉrʉku bhu umwʉyʉ, bhiijɨ amaheene ne eteemwa ɨnzʉmu kwa abhiisirirya. Na abhaangariri bhabhɨ na amanaga gu ukwanga amiija gʉʉsi gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ. Ɨkɨtabhʉ cha 1 Timoseo kɨna amangʼana maaru ganʉ gakʉsakirya abhakangati bha amasengerero sikʉ zɨnʉ kwimɨɨrɨrɨra amasengerero gaabhʉ.
\c 1
\s1 Amakeerenʼya
\p 
\v 1 Ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ nandikirɨ inyɨ Paaurʉ. Inyɨ nitumirwɨ kʉbha umutumwa\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Umutumwa\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \it abhatumwa\it* muKiniibhasa.\f* wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ, kwiswaja rya Mungu Ʉmʉsabhuri wɨɨtʉ na Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ ubhwisɨgi bhwɨtʉ.
\v 2 Nɨrakwandɨkɨra Timoseo, umwana waanɨ wa amaheene mubhwisirirya.
\p Ɨbhɨgʉngi no omorembe kurwa kwa Bhaabha Mungu na kwa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ, bhɨbhɨ na naawɨ.
\s1 Amaangirijʉ igʉrʉ wa amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ
\p 
\v 3 Hanʉ nabhuukirɨ kuja icharʉ cha Makɨdʉniya, nɨkakʉsabha wiikarɨ kʉrʉbhɨri rwa Efeeso. Nɨkakʉsabha, korereke ʉbhareche abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakwija amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ.
\v 4 Ʉbhareche bhatigɨ kugwatɨrɨra amaganʉ ganʉ gataana bhwera, na kwinyaacha kwitonda amariina ga bhasʉʉkʉrʉ, ganʉ gataana tɨnɨrʉ. Amangʼana gayo gʉʉsi garareeta zɨhaka, gatakʉsakirya abhaatʉ kwisirirya Mungu, chɨmbu ubhwɨndi bhwazɨ bhwʉ ʉkʉsabhʉra abhaatʉ.
\v 5 Ubhwɨndi bhwa amaswaja ganʉ nɨ‑kʉbha, abhiisirirya bhabhɨ nʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhu umwʉyʉ mwɨrʉ, ekoro nzɨrʉ nu ubhwisirirya bhwa amaheene.
\v 6 Nawe abhiija abhandɨ bhagatigirɨ gayo, bhiichurirɨ, bhasikiirɨ kʉgamba amangʼana ganʉ gataana bhwera.
\v 7 Bhareenda kʉbha abhiija bhi imigirʉ\f + \fr 1:7 \fk Abhiija bhi imigirʉ\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* ja Musa, nangabha ganʉ bhakʉgamba na kʉkandikija, bhatagɨɨzɨ.
\p 
\v 8 Nawe itwɨ tʉmɨnyirɨ imigirʉ ja Musa nɨ‑mɨzʉmu, arɨɨbhɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ aragituna chɨmbu ikwenderwa.
\v 9 Na toreenderwa komenya imigirʉ gɨtatɨɨrwɨ kobhe eheene, nawe kʉbhanʉ bhakʉkɨra imigirʉ na kʉbhaangi, bhanʉ bhatarɨ abhiisirirya na bhʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ, kʉbhanʉ bhatakwigwa Mungu na kʉbhabhɨ, kʉbhanʉ bhakwita bhawiisɨ na bhaunina, na kubhiiti bha abhaatʉ.
\v 10 Na gɨtɨɨrwɨ kʉ bhɨ ɨtaarʉ na bhanʉ bhakokora abhasubhɨ abhakɨndichabhʉ ncha abhakari, kubhiitɨgi bha abhaatʉ nʉ ʉkʉbhagurya mubhutumwa, abhabhɨɨhi, na kubhiirahiri bhʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ. Imigirʉ gɨtɨɨrwɨ kʉmangʼana gʉʉsi ganʉ gatakwigwana na amiija gʉ ʉbhʉhʉru.
\v 11 Amiija gayo, gahaabhoneka mʉNgʼana Ɨnzʉmu, yɨnʉ ikwerecha ʉbhʉgʉngʉ bhwa Mungu wʉ ʉrʉbhangʉ rwʉsi. Amangʼana gayo nego nahɨɨrwɨ na Mungu nɨraarɨkɨ.
\s1 Ʉrʉbhangʉ rwa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ kwa Paaurʉ
\p 
\v 12 Nɨrakumya Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ, Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ wʉnʉ aangʼɨɨrɨ zinguru, kʉ kʉbha akamenya moronge na akandobhora kʉbha omohocha waazɨ.
\v 13 Nangabha niizirɨ kʉmʉtʉka na kʉnyaacha abhaatʉ bhaazɨ, na naarɨ mʉsɨɨgʉ, nawe akandorera ɨbhɨgʉngi. Akakorabhu, kʉ kʉbha naarɨ nɨrakora gayo kobhogeege na nɨtaarɨ nu ubhwisirirya.
\v 14 Nɨ ɨbhɨgʉngi bhyʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ bhɨkakɨraho kwa niinyɨ. Na akangʼa ubhwisirirya nʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi ku ukugwatana neewe.
\p 
\v 15 Ringʼana rɨnʉ ni‑rya amaheene, na ereenderwa kwisiriribhwa bhʉkʉngʼu, “Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ akaaza kʉʉsɨ kʉsabhʉra bhʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ.” Kʉ bhayo, niinyɨ nɨkʉrirɨ ʉbhʉbhɨ kʉkɨra bhʉʉsi.
\v 16 Nʉʉrʉbhu, Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ akandorera ɨbhɨgʉngi! Akanyeerecha ubhwigumirirya bhwazɨ kwa niinyɨ kʉkɨra abhandɨ bhʉʉsi, korereke nɨbhɨ ekerenjo kʉbharya bhakumwisirirya na kʉsʉngʼaana ʉbhʉhʉru bhwa kemerano.
\v 17 Mungu newe Ʉmʉtɨmi wʉnʉ ataana ɨtɨnɨrʉ, atakukwa, na atakororekana, newe umwene. Ewe anu ubhusuukwa nʉ ʉbhʉgʉngʉ kemerano. Garamɨ.
\s1 Paaurʉ araswaja Timoseo kugwatɨrɨra amaswaja
\p 
\v 18 Timoseo mwana waanɨ, nɨrakoha riswaja riyo, kʉrɨngʼaana na amangʼana gʉ ʉbhʉrʉʉti ganʉ gaagambirwɨ igʉrʉ waazʉ. Amangʼana gayo gabhɨ ebheseme bhyazʉ kwitana riihɨ bhwaheene.
\v 19 Ugwatɨrɨrɨ ubhwisirirya ne ekoro nzɨrʉ. Abhaatʉ abhandɨ bhasiihiryɨ kokora garya bhɨɨzɨ ne‑heene riyo rigiriryɨ kutiga ubhwisirirya bhwabhʉ.
\v 20 Mʉbhaatʉ bhayo arimu Himɨnayo,\f + \fr 1:20a \xt 2 Timoseo 2:17‑18.\xt*\f* na Arɨkizanda. Bhayo nɨbhatigiirɨ Shɨtaani\f + \fr 1:20b \fk Nɨbhatigiirɨ Shɨtaani\ft , enzobhooro yaku nɨ‑Paaurʉ akaanga kongʼeha kugwatana na abhiisirirya mwisengerero.\f* korereke bhiijibhwɨ, bhatigɨ kʉmʉtʉka Mungu.
\c 2
\s1 Amiija igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉsɨngɨri bhwa risengerero
\p 
\v 1 Mmbe, ʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa gʉʉsi, nɨrasabha mʉbhɨ mʉrasabha igʉrʉ wa abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi, kʉmasabhi ga teemwa zʉʉsi. Na mʉbhɨ mʉrakumya Mungu igʉrʉ wa abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi.
\v 2 Ɨrabheenda kʉsabhɨra abhatɨmi na abhandɨ bhʉʉsi bhʉ ʉbhʉnaja, korereke twikarɨ komorembe, turiikara chɨmbu Mungu akwenda na kokora ganʉ gakwɨndibhwa mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwazɨ.
\v 3 Ringʼana rɨnʉ ni izʉmu, na rɨrazomera Mungu Ʉmʉsabhuri wɨɨtʉ.
\v 4 Ewe areenda abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi bhasabhurwɨ, na komenya amaheene.
\v 5 Areho Mungu wʉmwɨbhu, nu umwigwanʼya wa abhaatʉ na Mungu nɨ‑mʉʉtʉ wʉmwɨbhu, newe Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ.
\v 6 Ewe akahurucha ubhwikari bhwazɨ umwene, korereke asabhʉrɨ abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi. Bhʉnʉ nebhwe ʉbhʉmɨnyɨɨkɨrɨri bhʉnʉ Mungu atʉhɨɨrɨ, kwibhaga rɨnʉ atɨɨrɨ.
\v 7 Na kʉ kʉbha yiyo, niinyɨ natɨɨrwɨ umurwazi nu umutumwa. Nɨragamba ga amaheene, nɨtakʉgamba rʉrɨmɨ. Natɨɨrwɨ kʉbha umwija wa bhanʉ bhatarɨ Abhayaahudi, korereke nɨbhɨ nɨraraarɨka ɨngʼana yu ubhwisirirya na amaheene.
\p 
\v 8 Kʉgayo, ahagero hʉʉsi hanʉ mukwibhiringa kʉmʉsabha, nereenda abhasubhɨ bhanʉngɨ amabhoko igʉrʉ kʉmʉsabha. Bhakorebhu kubhwɨndi ʉbhʉzʉmu, bhasabhɨ bhatiigatɨɨnɨ naabha kʉhakaana.
\v 9 Ɨbhuɨbhu nereenda abhakari bhiibhohe koteemwa yɨnʉ ikwenderwa, bhabhɨ ne eteemwa nzʉmu ne ekerengo. Bhatasɨɨga ubhwʉgi bhwa kuniga zinzwɨrɨ, hamwɨ bhwa kwibhoha ebhegero bhyɨ ɨzahaabhu na bhɨnʉ bhɨkʉbharya, hamwɨ zengebho za riguri ikʉrʉ.
\v 10 Nawe bhabhɨ ne eteemwa nzʉmu chɨmbu ikwendwa kʉbhakari bhanʉ bhiisiriiryɨ kukumya Mungu.
\p 
\v 11 Hanʉ abhakari bhakʉbha bharɨɨga, bhabhɨ bhiikʉʉmu na bhiitɨgɨɨrɨri.
\v 12 Nɨtakʉbhaha abhakari umweya gwa kwija nʉʉrʉ kʉkangata abhasubhɨ, nawe bhabhɨ bhiikʉʉmu.
\v 13 Nɨrabhugabhu, kʉ kʉbha Mungu akakangata kʉbhʉmba Adaamu, akʉmara Haawa.
\v 14 Na Adaamu atakangiririibhwɨ, nawe ʉmʉkari newe akangiriribhwɨ, akakɨra umugirʉ gwa Mungu.\f + \fr 2:14 \xt Rora Ʉbhʉtangɨ 3:1‑6.\xt*\f*
\v 15 Nawe, abhakari bharasabhurwa kʉnzɨra yu ubhwibhuri bhwabhʉ, arɨɨbhɨ bharangʼeha kʉnaga mubhwisirirya, ʉbhʉsɨɨgi, ʉbhʉrɨndu na kʉbha ne eteemwa nzʉmu.
\c 3
\s1 Ubhwera bhwa abhaangariri bha risengerero
\p 
\v 1 Ringʼana rɨnʉ nɨ‑rya amaheene, “Ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ areenda emeremo jʉ ʉkʉbha umwangariri wa risengerero, wuyo igʉmbirɨ emeremo ɨmɨzʉmu.”
\v 2 Mmbe, umwangariri wa risengerero, abhɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ ataana isoro. Abhɨ musubhɨ wa mʉkari wʉmwɨ, abhɨ we ekerengo, naatu wa amangʼɨɨni, ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ akusuukwa, mwerya koro, nʉ ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ yɨɨzɨ kwija.
\v 3 Atabha munywi, atabha mwʉmani, abhɨ mʉnyʉʉhu wʉ ʉkʉsɨɨga omorembe. Na atabha mʉsɨɨgi wa mpirya.
\v 4 Abhɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ wu ukwimɨɨrɨrɨra bhwaheene inyumba yaazɨ, wʉnʉ yɨɨzɨ kotongera abhaana moteemwa yu ubhwisirirya nu ubhusuuku.
\v 5 Arɨɨbhɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ aratamwa kwimɨɨrɨrɨra inyumba yaazɨ umwene, aranajabhwɨ kuriibha abhaatʉ bha risengerero rya Mungu?
\v 6 Na atabha ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ isiriiryɨ Mungu haguhɨbhu, ataaza kwiheema. Kuyo kʉramokora atinirwɨ chɨmbu Shɨtaani\f + \fr 3:6 \fk Shɨtaani\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* aatiniirwɨ.
\v 7 Nawe, abhɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ akomenyeekererwa bhwaheene nʉʉrʉ na abhatamenya Mungu, bhataaza kuririirirwa na kʉhaatibhwa mwiheto rya Shɨtaani.
\s1 Ubhwera bhwa abhasakirya bha risengerero
\p 
\v 8 Abhasakirya bhʉʉsi, bhabhɨ bha teemwa nzʉmu, bhabhɨ bhagʉrʉrʉku, bhatabha bhanywi, bhatabha bhasɨɨgi bha mpirya.
\v 9 Nawe, bhabhɨ abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakugwatɨrɨra amaheene gu ubhwisirirya bhwɨtʉ kwa koro nzɨrʉ.
\v 10 Bhayo hinga bhagemwe. Na bharaarorekanɨ bhataana isoro, neho bhakore emeremo giyo.
\p 
\v 11 Kwikɨ abhakari bhaabhʉ\f + \fr 3:11 \fk Abhakari bhaabhʉ\ft , ʉbhʉgaruri ʉbhʉndɨ bhʉratʉra kʉbha, \fqa abhasakirya abhakari.\f* bhabhɨ bha teemwa nzʉmu, bhatabha bhagʉbhi bha abhaatʉ, bhabhɨ ne ekerengo no obhoronge mʉmangʼana gʉʉsi.
\v 12 Abhasakirya bhabhɨ nʉ ʉmʉkari wʉmwɨ, na bhabhɨ bhariimɨɨrɨrɨra bhwaheene abhaana bhaabhʉ na abhandɨ bhanʉ bhari munyumba yaabhʉ.
\v 13 Bharya bhakokora emeremo jʉ ʉbhʉsakirya bhwaheene, bharabha bharasuukwa. Hayo bharabha nʉ ʉbhʉkararu bhwʉ ʉkʉraganʼya ɨngʼana yu ubhwisirirya bhʉnʉ bhʉrɨ kwa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ.
\s1 Amaheene gu ubhwisirirya bhwɨtʉ
\p 
\v 14 Nɨrakwandɨkɨra amangʼana gayo, nangabha niriisega kuuza kwa naawɨ haguhɨbhu.
\v 15 Nawe nɨraakeezere, ʉramenya ganʉ gakobheenda abhaatʉ kokora munyumba ya Mungu. Abhaatʉ bhayo nebho risengerero rya Mungu wʉ ʉbhʉhʉru, na risengerero neryo ɨmbɨrʉ nʉ ʉbhʉrʉsa bhwa amaheene.
\v 16 Amaheene ganʉ Mungu ɨɨrɨkiryɨ, nɨ‑ga amateemo, nego nɨ‑ganʉ:
\q1 Kiriisitʉ akiiyerekenʼya kʉmʉbhɨrɨ,
\q1 akɨɨrɨkɨnibhwa ne Ekoro kʉbha moronge.
\q1 Akarorekana kwa bhamaraika,\f + \fr 3:16 \fk Bhamaraika\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \it maraika\it* muKiniibhasa.\f*
\q1 akarwazibhwa mubhyarʉ bhyʉsi.
\q1 Akiisiriribhwa kʉʉsɨ yʉʉsi,
\q1 akagegwa kuja igʉrʉ mʉbhʉgʉngʉ.
\c 4
\s1 Abhiija bhʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ
\p 
\v 1 Nangʉ Ekoro ɨragamba ɨtakubhisa, muzisikʉ za rusizʉ, abhandɨ bharatiga ubhwisirirya bhwa amaheene, na kutuna zekoro zʉ ʉbhʉkangirirya, na amiija ga Shɨtaani.
\v 2 Amiija gayo, gariijibhwa abhabhɨ, abhabhɨɨhi bhanʉ zekoro zaabhʉ zikuurɨ zangɨ nkina zʉchirwɨ ni ichʉma cho omorero.
\v 3 Bhayo bhararecha abhandɨ bhatigɨ kukwɨra, hamwɨ kurya ibhyakurya ɨbhɨndɨ. Nawe Mungu akabhɨbhʉmba korereke bhɨsʉngʼaanwɨ kubhukumya na abhiisirirya, kʉ kʉbha bhɨɨzɨ amaheene.
\v 4 Ebhegero bhyʉsi bhya Mungu, nɨ‑bhɨzʉmu, kɨtareeho cha kwangwa. Bhyʉsi bhɨsʉngʼaanwɨ kubhukumya,
\v 5 kʉ kʉbha ebhegero bhiyo bhɨbhɨngukiibhwɨ nɨ ɨngʼana ya Mungu na amasabhi gɨɨtʉ.
\s1 Omohocha ʉmʉzʉmu wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ
\p 
\v 6 Ʉraabhahɨ abhiisirirya bhʉʉsi amiija ganʉ, hayo neho ʉkʉbha omohocha ʉmʉzʉmu wa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ. Na ʉrabha ʉrɨrirwɨ bhwaheene mʉmaheene gu ubhwisirirya bhwɨtʉ na mumiija amazʉmu ganʉ ʉgatunirɨ.
\v 7 Ʉtaanɨ na amaganʉ ganʉ gatarɨ ga Mungu ganʉ gataana nzobhooro, nawe wiinaryɨ kwikara chɨmbu Mungu akwenda.
\v 8 Ɨmɨnyɨkɨɨnɨ, “Kʉnarya ʉmʉbhɨrɨ kobhona amanaga, kunu ubhwera bhusuuhubhu. Nawe, ukwinarya kwikara chɨmbu Mungu akwenda, kunu ubhwera bhwa teemwa zʉʉsi, kʉ kʉbha rɨnʉ rɨratoha ʉbhʉragɨ bhwo okobhona ʉbhʉhʉru bhwa nangwɨnʉ na bhʉnʉ bhukuuza.”
\v 9 Ringʼana riyo ni‑rya amaheene, na abhaatʉ bhareenderwa kʉrɨsʉngʼaana.
\v 10 Riyo neryo rikugirya turiikongʼeererya na kokora emeremo kumucha, kʉ kʉbha tʉramwisega Mungu wʉ ʉbhʉhʉru, Ʉmʉsabhuri wa abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi, kɨnda bhanʉ bhakumwisirirya.
\p 
\v 11 Amangʼana gayo, ugiijɨ na kʉgaswaja.
\v 12 Ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi atakorega kʉ kʉbha awɨ ʉkɨɨrɨ mumura, nawe okore umucha ʉbhɨ ekerenjo kubhiisirirya kʉkʉgamba, koteemwa, kʉbhʉsɨɨgi, kubhwisirirya no obhoronge.
\v 13 Kora umucha kosomera abhaatʉ Amaandɨkʉ Amarɨndu, na urwazɨ nu ukwija, kuhika hanʉ nikuuza iyo.
\v 14 Ʉtatiga kohokerya ʉbhʉnaja bhʉnʉ Mungu akʉhɨɨrɨ kʉhɨtɨra amangʼana gʉ ʉbhʉrʉʉti, hanʉ watɨɨrɨɨrwɨ amabhoko na abhiimiiririri bha risengerero.
\v 15 Ugwatɨ amangʼana gayo, korereke abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi bharore umucha gwazʉ mubhwikari bhwazʉ.
\v 16 Wangarɨrɨ eteemwa yaazʉ na amiija gaazʉ, na ongʼehe kokorabhu. Hanʉ okokora gayo uriisabhʉra awɨ aumwene na bhanʉ bhakukwitegeerera.
\c 5
\s1 Amaragɨrɨra kubhiisirirya
\p 
\v 1 Ʉtakanya ʉmʉkaruka, nawe omotongere chɨmbu ʉhaatongera wuusʉ. Abhamura ʉbhatongere ncha abhahiiri bhaazʉ,
\v 2 abhakari abhakɨkʉrʉ ncha onyoko, na abhaacha ncha abhasubhaati bhaazʉ. Okorebhu kumwʉyʉ mwɨrʉ.
\p 
\v 3 Ʉsʉʉkɨ abhakwirwa bhanʉ bhataana mʉsakirya.
\v 4 Nawe arɨɨbhɨ umukwirwa wʉwʉʉsi ana abhaana hamwɨ abhazʉkʉrʉ, bhayo bhɨɨgɨ kʉsakirya abhahiiri bhaabhʉ. Bharaakorebhu, neho bhakʉrɨha abhiibhuri bhaabhʉ amazʉmu ganʉ bhaabhakʉrɨɨrɨ. Ɨbhu nɨmbu Mungu akwenda.
\v 5 Ʉmʉkari umukwirwa wʉnʉ ataana ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉ ʉkʉmʉsakirya, wuyo ariisega Mungu, arasabha ʉbhʉsakirya kwa Mungu ubhutikʉ nu umwise.
\v 6 Nawe umukwirwa wʉnʉ asɨɨgirɨ amangʼana gɨ ɨɨsɨ, wuyo akuurɨ nangabha ararorekana mʉhʉru.
\v 7 Amaswaja gayo, ʉbhabhʉʉrɨrɨ abhiisirirya, korereke bhatabha ni isoro.
\v 8 Nawe ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi wʉnʉ atakʉsakirya abhaatʉ bhaazɨ, kɨnda bha yɨɨka waazɨ, wuyo arabha atigirɨ ubhwisirirya, na abhɨɨrɨ mʉbhɨ kʉkɨra ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ ataana ubhwisirirya.
\p 
\v 9 Umukwirwa ariisiriribhwa kʉbha mubhwɨndi bhwa abhakwirwa, arɨɨbhɨ ani imyaka kʉtangɨra merongo ɨsaasabha, naatu abhɨ aarɨ nu umusubhɨ wʉmwɨ.
\v 10 Abhɨ wu ubhukumya ʉbhʉzʉmu kʉmahocha gaazɨ amazʉmu. Abhɨ arɨrirɨ abhaana bhaazɨ bhwaheene, abhɨ aginihiryɨ abhagini, abhɨ ahʉkɨɨryɨ abhiisirirya ko kobhooja amagʉrʉ gaabhʉ, abhɨ abhasakiiryɨ bhanʉ bhakʉnyaakibhwa, na abhɨ akʉrirɨ amahocha gʉʉsi amazʉmu.
\p 
\v 11 Nawe abhakwirwa abhaacha, ʉtabhiisiririrya kusikɨra mubhwɨndi, kʉ kʉbha ɨnamba yʉ ʉmʉbhɨrɨ ɨrabhahiza kʉkɨra kwihurucha kwa Kiriisitʉ, bhayo bhareenda kukwɨrwa.
\v 12 Muriyo bharabha bhiirɨɨtɨɨrɨ zɨtɨnɨrʉ, kʉ kʉbha bhatigirɨ ʉbhʉragɨ bhwabhʉ kwa Kiriisitʉ bhwʉ ʉkʉsaaga bhaguru.
\v 13 Abhakwirwa ncha bhayo, bharanara eteemwa yʉ ʉbhʉtʉbhu, bharagendagenda muzinyumba za abhaatʉ. Kwikɨ, bharabha bhagwatanʼya na bhariisikirya mʉmangʼana ga abhandɨ, ɨnʉ bharagamba ganʉ gatakwenderwa.
\v 14 Mmbe, inyɨ nereenda abhakwirwa abhaacha, bhabhɨ bharakwɨrwa, bhiibhʉrɨ abhaana na kwangarɨra zinyumba zaabhʉ, korereke abhabhisa bhɨɨtʉ bhatatema amasoro.
\v 15 Rora kʉbha abhandɨ bhamarirɨ kʉbhʉra na kutuna Shɨtaani.
\p 
\v 16 Arɨɨbhɨ ʉmʉkari umwisirirya ana abhakwirwa mubhishoko bhyazɨ, abhasakiryɨ. Akorebhu, korereke risengerero ritigɨ kuhizwa, neho risengerero rɨrabha nu umweya gwʉ ʉkʉsakirya abhakwirwa abhandɨ bhanʉ bhataana ʉbhʉsakirya.
\p 
\v 17 Abhiimiiririri bhanʉ bhakwangarɨra risengerero bhwaheene, bhasuukwɨ na kokorerwa amazʉmu,\f + \fr 5:17 \fk Bhasuukwɨ na kokorerwa amazʉmu \ft kuKigiriki nɨ‑\fqa bhasuukwɨ manga kabhɨrɨ.\f* kɨnda bhanʉ bhakwihurucha kwerekeererya na kwija.
\v 18 Nɨrabhugabhu, kʉ kʉbha yandikirwɨ mʉMaandɨkʉ Amarɨndu, “Engʼombe hanʉ ɨkʉhʉʉra ɨnganʉ, ʉtayebhoha umunywa.”\f + \fr 5:18a \xt Rora Amahiityʉ gi Imigirʉ 25:4.\xt*\f* Na yandikirwɨ, “Omohocha areenderwa kurihwa ubhurihwa bhwazɨ.”\f + \fr 5:18b \xt Ruuka 10:7.\xt*\f*
\p 
\v 19 Utiisirirya ʉkʉgambwa kumwimiiririri wa risengerero, ʉkɨɨrɨ kʉbha na bhomenyeekererya bhwa abhaatʉ bhabhɨrɨ hamwɨ bhatatʉ.\f + \fr 5:19 \xt Rora Amahiityʉ gi Imigirʉ 17:6, 19:15.\xt*\f*
\v 20 Nawe abhiimiiririri bhanʉ bhakʉkaja kokora ʉbhʉbhɨ, ʉbhakanyɨ mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa bhʉʉsi, korereke na abhandɨ bhʉʉbhahɨ.
\s1 Amaangirijʉ kwa Timoseo
\p 
\v 21 Nɨrakuswaja mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Mungu, na mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ na bhamaraika abharobhorwa, ugwatɨrɨrɨ gayo, ʉtatɨnɨra kwa bhwangʉ hamwɨ kʉhɨngɨrɨra ʉrʉbhaara rʉmwɨ.
\v 22 Utiisirirya kwa bhwangʉ kʉtʉʉrɨra ʉmʉʉtʉ amabhoko komeremo jʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ, kʉ kʉbha ʉraatʉʉrɨ ʉmʉʉtʉ ʉmʉbhɨ momeremo giyo, na naawɨ ʉrabha ugwatɨɨnɨ mʉbhʉbhɨ bhwazɨ. Awɨ wiyangarɨrɨ, korereke ʉsaagɨ moronge.
\p 
\v 23 Kʉtangɨra nangwɨnʉ, awɨ ʉtanywa amanzi ageene, nawe ʉbhɨ ʉranywa ni idivaayi\f + \fr 5:23 \fk Idivaayi\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* hasuuhu, igʉrʉ wu ubhurwɨrɨ bhwazʉ bhwɨ ɨnda na amarwɨrɨ agandɨ ganʉ gakʉkʉnyaacha.
\p 
\v 24 Abhaatʉ abhandɨ, ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwabhʉ bhʉrarorekana habhwɨrʉ, nʉʉrʉ bhʉkɨɨrɨ kutinirwa. Nawe abhaatʉ abhandɨ, ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwabhʉ bhwibhisirɨ, bhʉrarorekana ibhaga rɨndɨ.
\v 25 Ɨbhuɨbhu, amahocha amazʉmu gararorekana habhwɨrʉ. Na garya gaarɨ gakɨɨrɨ giibhisirɨ, garabha habhwɨrʉ.
\c 6
\s1 Amaswaja kʉbhambʉʉsa abhiisirirya
\p 
\v 1 Bhambʉʉsa bhʉʉsi abhiisirirya, bhasʉʉkɨ abhakʉrʉ bhaabhʉ, korereke iriina rya Mungu na amiija gɨɨtʉ gataregwa.
\v 2 Bhambʉʉsa bhanʉ abhakʉrʉ bhaabhʉ ni‑bhiisirirya, bhatabharega kʉ kʉbha nɨ‑bhahiiri. Nawe bhareenderwa kʉbhakorera bhwaheene na kʉkɨraho, kʉ kʉbha bharabha bharasakirya abhiisirirya abhakɨndichabhʉ, na nɨ‑bhasɨɨgwa bhaabhʉ. Amangʼana gayo ugiijɨ na kʉbhakandikija.
\s1 Amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ nu ubhuniibhi bhwa amaheene
\p 
\v 3 Bhareho abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakwija amiija gʉ ʉrʉrɨmɨ. Bhariija ganʉ gatakwisiriranʼya na amiija gʉ ʉbhʉhʉru bhwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ, na gatakwisiriranʼya na amiija ganʉ gakʉkangata abhaatʉ kwikara chɨmbu Mungu akwenda.
\v 4 Bhayo bhiizwirɨ ubhwiyungi, na bhatɨɨzɨ ryʉryʉsi. Abhaatʉ bhayo bharʉʉmɨraku zɨhaka zɨnʉ zɨtaana bhwera igʉrʉ wɨ ɨhɨngʼana ihisuuhu. Na gayo gahaakora engʼeera, iryʉmana, amatuki na amiisɨɨgi amabhɨ,
\v 5 naatu sikʉ zʉʉsi garasarya ubhwigwani. Abhaatʉ bhayo bhasarikirɨ amangʼɨɨni, bhataana amaheene. Bhariisega ukwikara chɨmbu Mungu akwenda neyo ɨnzɨra yo okobhonera ubhuniibhi.
\p 
\v 6 Maheene, ukwikara chɨmbu Mungu akwenda kʉragirya ʉmʉʉtʉ abhɨ muniibhi bhʉkʉngʼu, kʉ kʉbha kʉramokora bhimwisɨ bhɨnʉ anabhyʉ.
\v 7 Garibhu kʉ kʉbha, mʉʉsɨ mʉnʉ tutiizirɨ na chʉchʉsi, na tʉtakʉbhʉʉka na chʉchʉsi.
\v 8 Mmbe, arɨɨbhɨ tuni ibhyakurya na bhyu ukwibhoha, twiswɨ na bhiyo.
\v 9 Nawe bhanʉ bhanu umwʉyʉ gu ubhuniibhi, bharagwɨra mubhitiimotiimo, na kʉhaatibhwa mwiheto, na mumwʉyʉ gwe ekegeege. Umwʉyʉ guyo gʉrabhasarya kuhika bharikɨ.
\v 10 Ʉkʉsɨɨga bhʉkʉngʼu zimpirya nekwe ʉbhʉtangɨ bhwʉ ʉbhʉbhɨ ubhwaru. Abhandɨ bhasɨɨgirɨ zimpirya na bhahabhirɨ, bhatigirɨ ubhwisirirya, nangʉ bhanʉ ʉbhʉsʉngʉ bhwaru nchʉ ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ akwisoma ne ekegeso.
\s1 Amaangirijʉ kwa Timoseo
\p 
\v 11 Nawe awɨ, ʉmʉʉtʉ wa Mungu, ʉgangʼose gayo. Utunɨ amaheene, wiikarɨ chɨmbu Mungu akwenda, ubhwisirirya, ʉbhʉsɨɨgi, ubhwigumirirya nu ubhusuuku.
\v 12 Ʉbhɨ nu umucha kutuna Mungu nʉʉrʉ ɨbhɨ bhʉkʉngʼubhwɨ, korereke ugwatɨrɨrɨ ʉbhʉhʉru bhwa kemerano. Ʉbhʉhʉru bhuyo nebhwe wabhirikiriirwɨ, hanʉ wiisiriiryɨ ubhwisirirya bhwazʉ mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa abhamɨnyɨɨkɨrɨri bhaaru.
\v 13 Nɨrakuswaja mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Mungu wʉnʉ akoha ʉbhʉhʉru ebhegero bhyʉsi, na mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ wʉnʉ aahurukiryɨ obhomenyeekererya bhwa amaheene mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Pʉntiyʉ Piraato, kʉbha,
\v 14 ugwatɨrɨrɨ amaswaja gayo kwa kugiisirirya, ʉtabha ni isoro, kuhika hanʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ akuuza.
\v 15 Ukuuza kwazɨ kʉrabha ribhaga rɨnʉ ɨɨndirɨ Mungu. Mungu wʉ ʉrʉbhangʉ rwʉsi, nʉ ʉmʉkangati umwene, newe Ʉmʉtɨmi wa abhatɨmi nʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wa abhakʉrʉ.
\v 16 Ewe, newe arabha iikɨɨrɨ mubhwɨrʉ bhʉnʉ ʉmʉʉtʉ atakʉtʉra kubhwisukɨra. Na atareeho ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ amʉrʉʉzɨ, nʉʉrʉ wʉnʉ akʉtʉra komorora. Ubhusuuku na amanaga gabhɨ kwewe, kemerano. Garamɨ.
\p 
\v 17 Ʉbhabhʉʉrɨrɨ abhaniibhi bhatigɨ kwikumya, nʉʉrʉ kwisega ubhuniibhi bhwabhʉ bhwɨ ɨɨsɨ yɨnʉ, bhʉnʉ ni‑bhwi ibhaga isuuhu. Nawe bhiisege Mungu wʉnʉ akotoha ebhegero bhyʉsi kwe ekoro nzɨrʉ, korereke tobhehokerye kwa bhozomerwa.
\v 18 Na ʉbhabhʉʉrɨrɨ bhakore amazʉmu, neho bhabhɨ abhaniibhi mʉmahocha amazʉmu. Bhabhɨ bha koro nzʉmu na kugwatanʼya na abhandɨ ebhegero bhyabhʉ.
\v 19 Ko kokorabhu, bhariitʉʉrɨra ikibhumbɨkʉ kɨnʉ kɨkʉbha ʉbhʉrʉsa ʉbhʉnagu kuzisikʉ zɨnʉ zikuuza. Hayo neho bhakʉsʉngʼaana ʉbhʉhʉru bhwa amaheene.
\p 
\v 20 Timoseo, gwatɨrɨra bhwaheene ɨngʼana ye eheene yɨnʉ wahɨɨrwɨ. Utigɨ kwisikirya mʉmangʼana ganʉ gataana nzobhooro yʉyʉʉsi. Kwikɨ utiisikirya na zɨhaka ze ekegeege, zɨnʉ abhandɨ bhakubhuga nezo ʉbhʉmɨnyi.
\v 21 Abhaatʉ abhandɨ bhanʉ bhagwatiriirɨ gayo, bhatigirɨ ubhwisirirya bhwabhʉ.
\p Ɨbhɨgʉngi bhɨbhɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niimwɨ.
